What is xray?
key features and benifits

Xray Test Management
  •	Xray for Jira is a comprehensive test management app that allows teams to manage their testing life cycle – planning, design, execution and reporting. 
  •	It supports both manual and automated testing (like BDD with Cucumber, Jenkins, GitLab), provides custom reports
•	
Key features and benefits
  •	Jira native integration
  •	Manual and automated testing 
  •	Full test lifecycle management
  •	Traceability
  •	Dashboards and reports

configuration of xray in jira
  Configuring Xray in Jira involves two main stages : installing the Xray app from the Atlassian Marketplace and then configuring the settings within your specific
  Jira project
  Stage 1: Installation (Jira Administrator Required): navigate to apps and find for xray test management and install it for free trail
  Stage 2: Project Configuration : automatic configuration for company based projects and manula configurations forn team based project management of issues tyeps
  
  
